paragraphs.title: score model on training sample
paragraphs.text:
%python
data = train_data
X = data[x_cols]
y = data[target]
import sklearn as skl
df = model.predict(X, supplemental_cols=data).pull()
df = df.rename({'PREDICTION':'PREDICTION_automl'}, axis=1)
df['FRACTIONAL_ERROR'] = np.abs((df[target] - df.PREDICTION_automl)/df[target])
print ('df.shape = ', df.shape)
y_true = df[target]
y_pred = df['PREDICTION_automl']
score = skl.metrics.r2_score(y_true, y_pred)
print('r2 = ', score)
score = skl.metrics.mean_absolute_error(y_true, y_pred)
print('mean_absolute_error = ', score)
median_fractional_error = (np.abs((y_true - y_pred)/y_true)).median()
print ('median_fractional_error = ', median_fractional_error)
cols = [case_id, target, 'PREDICTION_automl', 'FRACTIONAL_ERROR']
df_train_predictions = df
df_train_predictions[cols].sample(5)

paragraphs.title: compute mean predictions & actuals across logarithmic bins
paragraphs.text:
%python
Nbins = 101
df = df_test_predictions
df = df[[case_id, target, 'AUTOML']].copy()
df['log_SALE_PRICE'] = np.log(df.SALE_PRICE)
df['bin'] = df.log_SALE_PRICE - df.log_SALE_PRICE.min()
df.bin /= df.bin.max()
df.bin *= Nbins
df.bin = df.bin.astype(int)
agger = {'TRANSACTION_ID':'count', 'SALE_PRICE':['mean', 'std'], 'AUTOML':['mean', 'std']}
df = df.groupby('bin').agg(agger).reset_index()
df['N_RECORDS'] = df['TRANSACTION_ID']['count']
df['SALE_PRICE_MEAN'] = df['SALE_PRICE']['mean']
df['SALE_PRICE_SIGMA'] = df['SALE_PRICE']['std']/np.sqrt(df['N_RECORDS'])
df['AUTOML_MEAN'] = df['AUTOML']['mean']
df['AUTOML_SIGMA'] = df['AUTOML']['std']/np.sqrt(df['N_RECORDS'])
cols = ['N_RECORDS', 'SALE_PRICE_MEAN', 'SALE_PRICE_SIGMA', 'AUTOML_MEAN', 'AUTOML_SIGMA']
df = df[cols]
df.columns = cols
print ('df.shape = ', df.shape)
df_test_binned = df
df_test_binned.sample(3)

paragraphs.title: plot fractional error in mean predictions
paragraphs.text:
%python
df = df_test_binned
idx = (df.N_RECORDS > 1)
dfs = df[idx]
xp = dfs.SALE_PRICE_MEAN/1.0e6
yp = ( dfs.AUTOML_MEAN - dfs.SALE_PRICE_MEAN)/dfs.SALE_PRICE_MEAN
err = np.sqrt(dfs.SALE_PRICE_SIGMA**2 + dfs.AUTOML_SIGMA**2)/dfs.SALE_PRICE_MEAN
fig, ax = plt.subplots(1,1, figsize=(16, 6))

yp = yp*0

p = ax.set_ylim(-0.4, 0.6)

paragraphs.title: calculate fractional error versus record fraction
paragraphs.text:
%python
df = df_test_predictions
df = df[[case_id, target, 'AUTOML', 'FRACTIONAL_ERROR']].copy()
df = df.sort_values('FRACTIONAL_ERROR')
df['all'] = 1
df['all_record_fraction'] = df['all'].cumsum()/len(df)
df = df.drop('all', axis=1)
df['middle'] = 0
idx = (df[target] > 4.5e5) & (df[target] < 1.1e6)
print ('central fraction = ', idx.sum()/len(idx))
df = df[idx]
df['middle'] = 1
df['middle_record_fraction'] = df['middle'].cumsum()/len(df)
df = df.drop('middle', axis=1)
df.sample(3)

paragraphs.title: compute feature importance
paragraphs.text:
%python
train = oml.sync(table='BROOKLYN_TRAIN')
x = train[x_cols]
y = train[target]
print ('x.shape, y.shape = ', x.shape, y.shape)
setting = {'ODMS_SAMPLING':'ODMS_SAMPLING_DISABLE'}
feature_importance_model = oml.ai(**setting)
feature_importance_model = feature_importance_model.fit(x, y)
df = feature_importance_model.importance.pull()
df.importance /= df.importance.sum()
feature_importance = df
